name: Time Cafe Nusa Penida
address: sebunibus, Sakti, Kec. Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: This place is amazing! The staff are so welcoming and the food is incredible. We got talking with one of the staff and she set us up with a private driver for the time we were on the island! I highly recommend the food, the smoothies are great- this is a must visit :)
review 2: During our stay in Nusa, we decided to give this restaurant a try, and became regulars as we both loved the food and how welcoming the staff were. The four days we stayed in Nusa Penida we had at least one meal a day here and became exited to go again as we were welcomed with smiles and conversation along with yummy food.
review 3: This place just opened and beside of the main road, the food was amazing, they have mexican, local, and i was tried their happy burger, was really yummy. Will come back again try their local food. The staff was so friendly and spoke really well english.
review 4: I really enjoyed their Indonesian food, they served with different way with Indonesian food i have tried before. There is chicken satay also in their nasi goreng. This is the best nasi goreng that I ever had. They also provide mexican food. This place is really recommended.
review 5: It was delicious food. They just opened, I ordered nasi goreng and my friend  thier mexican food. All was great, and cheap.This place is recommended. Will be back again
